gate: OPEN
task: S75-TE2
title: Verify and Fix Reports Screen End-to-End
description: |
  Verify the complete reports flow works against old app feature parity.

  OLD APP REPORTS FEATURES (iOS ReportVC + Android ReportFragment):
    - Select report type (from API: GET /ws/reports returns ReportItem[] with bunchId)
    - Select company (GET /ws/getcompanies)
    - Select vehicle(s) — multi-select, filtered by company
    - Set date range: From / Until
    - Press "Generate" → POST /ws/reports/v2/request
    - Show progress via SSE: GET /ws/reports/v2/state?token=
    - Show completed report (download / view as JSON)
    - Report history: GET /ws/reports/v2/list
    - Delete report: DELETE /ws/reports/v2/:id
    - Download: GET /ws/reports/v2/:id/:type (json/xlsx/pdf)

  VERIFICATION CHECKLIST:
    1. Open Reports tab → ReportsScreen renders without error
    2. Report type dropdown populates from GET /ws/reports (not hardcoded list)
    3. Company dropdown populates from GET /ws/getcompanies
       IMPORTANT: API returns {key, value} objects — map key→id, value→name
       (Bug previously in sprint 69: raw response caused companyIds:[null])
    4. Vehicle dropdown filters to selected company (or shows all if no company)
    5. Date pickers work
    6. "Generate" sends correct payload to POST /ws/reports/v2/request:
         { bunchId, vehicleIds, companyIds, fromDate, toDate }
       companyIds must NOT be null/undefined — use company.key values
    7. SSE progress stream connects and shows progress % to user
    8. Report completes and result is displayed / downloadable
    9. Report history list shows previously generated reports
    10. Delete button removes a report from the list

  FIX ANY FAILURES found during verification.

acceptance:
  - Report type list loads from API dynamically
  - Company and vehicle selectors are populated and functional
  - Report generation sends valid payload and receives response
  - SSE progress indicator updates while report is building
  - Completed report can be viewed or downloaded
  - Report history is displayed and deletable

requires: [FRONTEND_DEV]
estimated: 2.5 hours
